title: Elvis Presley - Complete 1954-1962 USA Singles (4CD-Box 2015)
description:
Limited-edition 4 CD set comprising the complete Presley singles and EPs released in the USA up to 1962 presented in the order in which they were issued. This edition comes with a comprehensive booklet full of discographical information, rare photos and memorabilia. Eight tracks have been added as a bonus making 100 songs recorded by Elvis in his prime 

Elvis Presley - ELVIS: The Complete 1954-1962 U.S.A. Singles
Label: Valentine Records - 47772
Format: 4 x CD, Compilation, Box Set, Remastered, Limited Edition
Country: UK
Released: 2015
Genre: Rock
Style: Rock'n'Roll, Ballads, Pop
